CSCI321, Fall 2017, Pop Quiz \#3


In Blender you can create game logic without programming
using sensors, controllers, and actuators.
\begin{enumerate}

\item Give one example of a Blender {\bf Sensor} and
  briefly explain what it does.
  \vfill
  
\item Give one example of a Blender {\bf Controller} and
  briefly explain what it does.
  \vfill
  
\item Give one example of a Blender {\bf Actuator} and
  briefly explain what it does.
  \vfill
  
\end{enumerate}

